---
layout: base.njk
title: Editorials
title_nl: Columns
title_fr: Éditoriaux
description: Original articles by Rik Van Bruggen about the Positron Today project, philosophy, and the pursuit of positive news.
---

<style>
  .editorials-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .editorials-header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 2rem); font-weight: 800;
    color: #451a03; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .editorials-header p {
    font-size: 0.95rem; color: #b45309; max-width: 42rem; line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .editorial-list {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;
  }
  .editorial-card {
    background: white; border: 2px solid #c084fc; border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem; text-decoration: none; color: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
  }
  .editorial-card:hover {
    border-color: #a855f7; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.15);
  }
  .editorial-card-emoji { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }
  .editorial-card-title {
    font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #581c87; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .editorial-card-date {
    font-size: 0.75rem; color: #7e22ce; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .editorial-card-summary {
    font-size: 0.875rem; color: #451a03; line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .editorials-empty {
    text-align: center; padding: 3rem; color: #b45309; font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
</style>

<div class="editorials-header">
  <h1>
    <span class="t-en">✍️ Editorials</span>
    <span class="t-nl" style="display:none">✍️ Columns</span>
    <span class="t-fr" style="display:none">✍️ Éditoriaux</span>
  </h1>
  <p>
    <span class="t-en">Original articles by Rik Van Bruggen about the Positron Today project, the philosophy behind it, and the pursuit of positive news.</span>
    <span class="t-nl" style="display:none">Originele artikelen van Rik Van Bruggen over het Positron Today project, de filosofie erachter, en de zoektocht naar positief nieuws.</span>
    <span class="t-fr" style="display:none">Articles originaux de Rik Van Bruggen sur le projet Positron Today, la philosophie qui le sous-tend, et la quête d'informations positives.</span>
  </p>
</div>

{% set editorialPosts = collections.editorials %}
{% if editorialPosts.length > 0 %}
<div class="editorial-list">
  {% for post in editorialPosts %}
  <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="editorial-card">
    <div class="editorial-card-emoji">{{ post.data.emoji if post.data.emoji else "✍️" }}</div>
    <div class="editorial-card-title">
      <span class="t-en">{{ post.data.title }}</span>
      <span class="t-nl" style="display:none">{{ post.data.title_nl if post.data.title_nl else post.data.title }}</span>
      <span class="t-fr" style="display:none">{{ post.data.title_fr if post.data.title_fr else post.data.title }}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="editorial-card-date">{{ post.date | dateDisplay }}</div>
    <div class="editorial-card-summary">
      <span class="t-en">{{ post.data.summary }}</span>
      <span class="t-nl" style="display:none">{{ post.data.summary_nl if post.data.summary_nl else post.data.summary }}</span>
      <span class="t-fr" style="display:none">{{ post.data.summary_fr if post.data.summary_fr else post.data.summary }}</span>
    </div>
  </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
{% else %}
<div class="editorials-empty">
  <span class="t-en">No editorials published yet. Stay tuned!</span>
  <span class="t-nl" style="display:none">Nog geen columns gepubliceerd. Binnenkort meer!</span>
  <span class="t-fr" style="display:none">Aucun éditorial publié pour le moment. Restez connecté !</span>
</div>
{% endif %}
